com.facebook.buck.rules.args

Interface Arg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AddsToRuleKey, RuleKeyAppendable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileListableLinkerInputArg, FrameworkPathArg, MacroArg, ProxyArg, RelativeLinkArg, RustLibraryArg, SanitizedArg, SourcePathArg, StringArg, StringWithMacrosArg, ThinArchiveArg, WorkerMacroArg

    public interface Arg
extends RuleKeyAppendable
    An abstraction for modeling the arguments that contribute to a command run by a BuildRule, and also carry information for computing a rule key.

      • appendToCommandLine

        void appendToCommandLine(com.google.common.collect.ImmutableCollection.Builder<String> builder,
                         SourcePathResolver pathResolver)
        Append the contents of the Arg to the supplied builder. This call may inject any number of elements (including zero) into the builder. This is only ever safe to call when the rule is running, as it may do things like resolving source paths.
